data.description: Seller is willing to pay up to $5,000 towards buyer's closing costs! Built in 2019, this home is located in the gated community of Northgate! This two story family home offers 1965 sq ft of living area with 3 bedrooms (loft could be used as 4th bedroom), 2.5 baths and a 2 car garage. This home has 9' ceilings and is neat and clean and ready to move in! There is a half bath on the first floor. The kitchen includes all stainless appliances, a pantry, and a large island. The master bedroom is large and has a walk in closet- and the master bath has a walk in shower upgrade. There are hurricane shutters for all windows. The home also features a covered patio for grilling, and a nice privacy fenced backyard with plenty of room for the kids and pets to play. You will also love the huge community swimming pool- great for swimming laps or just cooling off in the summertime. The home is conveniently located near US 301, US Hwy 41, I-75, and world class beaches, boat ramps, golfing, shopping, restaurants and entertainment. Pets are welcome... and no CDD!
